messages.content: What is the price of apple pie in the bakery?

I'm sorry, I don't have access to real-time information, including bakery prices.  To tell you the price of an apple pie, I need to know which bakery you're asking about.  Which bakery are you referring to?
ஐ அம் டாகிங் அபவுட் தி பேக்கரி இன் பேங்களூரு.
I'm talking about the bakery in Bangalore.
